Interface IDVOffPrint

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DVOffPrint

    public interface IDVOffPrint
    Offline print engine instance. Useful for reporting featurees that don't require initializing an online host. For example, printing PEM encoded X.509 certificates.

    Milton Smith
